de.avgl.dmp.converter.functional

Interface UnitFunction2<T,U>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of first input parameter
    U - Type of second input parameter

    public interface UnitFunction2<T,U>
    Functional interface for any binary function(x, y) that operates on any x of type T and any y of type U, presumably introducing side effects. The function returns void, which is denoted as UnitFunction.
    Author:
    Paul Horn
